Two package options for building Shiny dashboards: flexdashboard and shinydashboard

FLEXDASHBOARD
1. Use R Markdown to publish a group of related data visualizations as a dashboard
2. Support a wide variety of components
3. Flexible and easy to specify row and colun-based layouts
4. Offer storyboard layouts for presenting sequences
5. Optionally use Shiny to drive visualizations dynamically

